ow that im much older i have had some very cool exotic animals i have had ring tailed lemurs lesser bush babies prairie dogs and my favorite right now are my skunks so why is this scott smiths all animal expo well lee watson and i were talking about his show the watsons reptile swap he was trying to find a new location to have his show because he had just sold his property i found a place at the dupage county fairgrounds and lee took me in as his partner together we turned it into the scott smiths all animal expo they say if you like your job you never have to work a day in your life i absolutely love what i do with the show to me its about educating people i love the look on a childs face when they find the animal that is meant for them please feel free to ask me any question you would like…even how tall i am latest news brian barczyk at the expo this sunday  july    no comments last minute road trip to the all animal expo for brian barczyk ok sure why not brian barczyk of discovery channel’s venom hunters and his weekly web show snakebytestv will be visiting us this sunday   come on out and you just might get a chance to snag a pic or talk with bryan while … read more table top and pet chicken show july st  june    no comments the chicago spirit serama club is holding a table top competition at our show on saturday july st with ribbons and trophies for all the winners  everyone with a chicken of any type is welcome to enter the pet chicken and dressed upchicken contests which are always a ton of fun  click on the links … read more kangaroos return to the all animal expo sunday june th june    no comments didn’t get a chance to take a picture with the kangaroo’s last time  heard about the kangaroo’s after the fact and wished you would have come  sunday june th is your chance to come see and hold a baby kangaroo  check out our pictures page to see some visitors with the awesome marsupials  scott smith’s … read more important  show information re live  frozen rats fe