us will also be at the show this weekend  so bring the family to see some amazing animals help some of our animal friends and let santa know how good you’ve been this year as always doors open for the all animal expo at  am and we are open until  pm  admission  yrs  up visitors w animals  admission kids   under free wpaid adult free parking food available on site atm available on site share thisclick to email this to a friend opens in new windowclick to share on facebook opens in new windowclick to share on twitter opens in new windowclick to share on pinterest opens in new windowclick to share on google opens in new windowmoreclick to print opens in new window previous article  all animal expo dates next article brian barczyk of discovery channel’s new series venom hunters upcoming shows all animal expo august    am   pm all animal expo august    am   pm all animal expo september    am   pm all animal expo september    am   pm view all events contact information  email protected  manchester road wheaton il dupage county fairgrounds all animal show supporters send to email address your name your email address cancel post was not sent  check your email addresses email check failed please try again sorry your blog cannot share posts by email scott smith createexplorelearn  supportget startedlog inpricingget startedlog inmy prezisexplorelearn  supportproductcompanycareerssupportcommunitycontactappsenglishespañol한국어deutschportuguêsfrançaismagyaritaliano scott smiths public prezis go to profile page ›decreasing procastination by scott smith on  february  reusableuntitled prezi by scott smith on  february  reusableuntitled prezi by scott smith on  february  reusabled by scott smith on  january  reusable d biomass energy by scott smith on  january  reusable eilidhs science project copy of sound engineering by scott smith on  january  reusable scott and andrew physics sound engineering by scott smith on  november  reusable scott and andrew physics sound engineering by scott